      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation must be the same quantities used to support the device safety decision.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis is the primary regulatory QoI for CPB device submissions per FDA guidance. The same scalar hemolysis metric is used in both validation comparisons and worst-case operating condition identification."
